Brain Drain Beam*
Causes your wizard to emit a beam of Brain Draining.  All creatures in the
chosen direction will lose 10 points of intelligence.  Any creature thus
reduced to less than 0 intelligence will die.  The Brain Drain Beam affects
your own creatures as well as your enemies, so be careful where you cast
it.

This spell does not affect inanimate objects, growths or scrolls.
